Title: Sedition
Description:
<The poster reads:>

MERRIX is CORRUPT! STEELVEIN is WEAK!

They cannot protect the earthen! They do not care about them! They spit upon the Edicts!

Merrix was BRIBED to reopen Steelvein's smuggling operation! Steelvein HIDES behind Merrix's authority!

They are taking from YOUR pockets to line THEIRS!

DO NOT TRUST THEIR LIES!
ObjectivesText: Speak to Merrix at the Councilward's Rise in Dornogal.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak to Merrix at the Councilward's Rise in Dornogal.
RewardText:
Yes, I am quite aware of the situation.

It has rather disrupted my morning.
